=== 一級方程式賽車 ===
[[File:Daniel_Ricciardo_2011_Malaysia_FP1_1.jpg|thumb]]里卡多身為[[紅牛二隊|紅牛二隊]]的三號車手]]

在2009年12月1日至3日，於[[赫雷斯賽道|赫雷斯賽道]]為期三天的[[紅牛車隊|紅牛車隊]]青年車手測試，里卡多首次駕駛[[一級方程式|一級方程式]]賽車<ref>{{en}}{{cite news | authors = Beer, Matt; Noble, Jonathan | date = 2009-11-09 | accessdate = 2009-11-10 | title = Red Bull to give Ricciardo first F1 test | work = autosport.com | publisher = Haymarket Publications | url = http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/80105 | archive-date = 2017-08-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170808121758/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/80105 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。在測試的最後一天，他以超過一秒的時間締造了最速時間。使他成為唯一進入1:17門檻的車手<ref>{{en}}{{cite news | first = Jamie | last = O'Leary | date = 2009-12-03 | accessdate = 2009-12-03 | title = Ricciardo ends Jerez test on top | work = autosport.com | publisher = Haymarket Publications | url = http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/80428 | archive-date = 2016-09-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160910220924/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/80428 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。[[紅牛車隊|紅牛車隊]]的主席[[克里斯蒂安·霍內爾|克里斯蒂安·霍內爾]]建議說里卡多能夠取代他2010年世界系列賽的隊友[[布蘭登·哈特利|哈特利]]成為車隊的測試與替補車手<ref>{{en}}{{cite news | first = Jamie | last = O'Leary | date = 2009-12-02 | accessdate = 2009-12-04 | title = Ricciardo eyes Red Bull test role | work = autosport.com | publisher = Haymarket Publications | url = http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/80398 | archive-date = 2016-09-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160910223057/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/80398 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。最後結果是里卡多與哈特利兩人共享車隊與姐妹隊[[紅牛二隊|紅牛二隊]]的測試及替補責任<ref>{{en}}{{cite news | url = http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/81063 | title = Ricciardo, Hartley to be Red Bull reserves | first = Jonathan | last = Noble | work = autosport.com | publisher = Haymarket Publications | date = 2010-01-26 | accessdate = 2010-01-27 | archive-date = 2010-01-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100129214929/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/81063 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，直到後者離開紅牛少年車隊（Red Bull Junior team）<ref>{{en}}{{cite news | url = http://www.gpupdate.net/en/f1-news/239300/hartley-dropped-as-red-bull-reserve-driver/ | title = Hartley Dropped as Red Bull Reserve Driver | work = GPUpdate.net | publisher = GPUpdate.net | date = 2010-07-21 | accessdate = 2010-10-16 | archive-date = 2016-09-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160910214108/http://www.gpupdate.net/en/f1-news/239300/hartley-dropped-as-red-bull-reserve-driver/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

2010年11月11日，里卡多被證實成為[[紅牛車隊|紅牛車隊]]季末的青年測試車手，將在11月16日—17日於[[亞斯碼頭賽道|亞斯碼頭賽道]]代表車隊出賽。根據報導，他說道「我迫不及待要駕駛紅牛車隊驚人的一級方程式賽車來發出猛烈攻擊。」（"I can't wait to get another crack at driving Red Bull Racing's amazing Formula One car."）<ref>{{cite news|date=2010-11-11|accessdate=2010-11-11|title=Ricciardo to star for Red Bull at young driver test|work=formula1.com|publisher=[[Formula_One_Group|Formula One Administration]]|url=http://www.formula1.com/news/headlines/2010/11/11504.html|archive-date=2014-04-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140408214503/http://www.formula1.com/news/headlines/2010/11/11504.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>里卡多持續展現出他單圈的超凡技術並且主宰了這場賽事。他的最快單圈比[[2010年世界一級方程式錦標賽|2010年]]世界冠軍[[賽巴斯蒂安·維泰爾|賽巴斯蒂安·維泰爾]]於週六排位賽的成績快了1.3秒。<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|first=Edd|last=Straw|date=2010-11-17|accessdate=2010-11-17|title=Ricciardo dominates rookie testing|work=autosport.com|publisher=Haymarket Publications|url=http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/88355|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304002907/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/88355|dead-url=no}}</ref>
