iardo's disqualification|first=Paul|last=Weaver|work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]|publisher=[[Guardian_Media_Group|Guardian Media Group]]|date=2014-03-16|accessdate=2014-03-21|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111212910/https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2014/mar/16/red-bull-australia-grand-prix-daniel-ricciardo|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 [[国际汽车联合会|-{zh-tw:國際汽車聯盟;zh-cn:国际汽车联合会;zh-hk:國際汽車聯合會;zh-sg:国际汽车联合会}-]]在4月14日審理過後，駁回上訴並維持原來裁决<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|url=https://www.skysports.com/f1/news/12475/9266769|title=FIA reject Red Bull appeal and uphold decision of stewards to exclude Ricciardo|first=Pete|last=Gill|work=[[Sky_Sports|Sky Sports]]|publisher=[[Sky_Group_Limited|Sky Group Limited]]|date=2014-04-15|accessdate=2020-09-08|archive-date=2020-11-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124091120/https://www.skysports.com/f1/news/12475/9266769|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

