==個人生活==
里卡多為[[意大利|意大利]]裔澳洲人，他的父親生於[[西西里島|西西里島]][[菲卡拉|菲卡拉]]，<ref>{{cite news|title=Daniel Ricciardo awarded the Trofeo Lorenzo Bandini for his speed, success and attitude in Formula 1|url=http://www.foxsports.com.au/motor-sport/formula-one/daniel-ricciardo-awarded-the-trofeo-lorenzo-bandini-for-his-speed-success-and-attitude-in-formula-1/story-e6frf3zl-1227044733111|accessdate=2015-02-11|work=FOX SPORTS|date=2014-09-02|archive-date=2014-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140906220542/http://www.foxsports.com.au//motor-sport/formula-one/daniel-ricciardo-awarded-the-trofeo-lorenzo-bandini-for-his-speed-success-and-attitude-in-formula-1/story-e6frf3zl-1227044733111|dead-url=no}}</ref>而他的母親則來自於[[卡拉布里亞|卡拉布里亞]]。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.grandprix.com.au/news/italian-background-australian-through-and-through |title=Italian background, Australian through and through |publisher=Australian Formula 1 Grand Prix |accessdate=2014-08-31 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140901084725/http://www.grandprix.com.au/news/italian-background-australian-through-and-through |archivedate=2014-09-01 }}</ref>

里卡多表示對於英語使用者他會說他的姓為“里卡-{}-多”，他的家人也總是這麼念，而不是在[[紅牛二隊|紅牛二隊]]中以義大利語發音的“里奇亞-{}-多”。<ref name="Pron"/>

在参加著名汽车节目[[Top_Gear|Top Gear]]的第22季第3集的节目里，里卡多以1：42.02的成绩超越[[刘易斯·汉密尔顿|刘易斯·汉密尔顿]]成为该节目“一级方程式车手开平价车”环节中最快圈速的创造者。<ref>[https://twitter.com/redbullracing/status/564524257133465600 @ReadBullRacing: What a lap! Daniel's time of 1:42.2 sends him to the top of the @BBC_TopGear #F1 leaderboard. ] {{Wayback|url=https://twitter.com/redbullracing/status/564524257133465600 |date=20200313162121 }}.@redbullracing.Twitter.2015-02-09.[2015-02-09]</ref>

里卡多受到澳大利亚摩托车赛手{{le|杰克·米勒(摩托车手)|Jack Miller (motorcycle racer)|杰克·米勒}}启发和影响，从2016年赛季的[[2016年德国大奖赛|德国站]]开始，他在获得领奖台后都会将香槟酒灌入自己的鞋子中并喝下，他管这种庆祝形式称为“{{le|Shoey|Drinking from shoes}}”；除了他自己喝下以外，他也会让赛后采访的主持人和同上领奖台的车手喝下。

